OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with late sunny spells
OL,7,Fleading to clear spells after sunset.
OL,8,FOvernight remaining dry with any cloud
OL,9,Fclearing to give clear skies. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry morning with bright
OL,13,Fand sunny spells. Turning cloudier
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon with light rain
OL,15,Fspreading eastwards through the
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
